            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Slice the two ends from the <strong>turkey</strong> <strong>wellington<span class=\"text-danger\">[s]</strong> </span>and slice into 4 <span class=\"text-danger\">[8]</span> slices</p><p>Serve the <strong>sliced turkey wellington</strong> with the <strong>mash</strong> and <strong>garlic cavolo nero</strong> to the side</p><p>Drizzle over the <strong>mustard gravy</strong></p><p>Enjoy!</p>",
